name: Query1
body: SELECT email FROM Lecturer WHERE Lecturer_id = 'Huong'

name: Query2
body: SELECT DISTINCT email FROM Lecturer JOIN (SELECT * FROM Enrollment WHERE students = 'Thanh' AND lecturers = 'Huong' ) AS TEMP ON TEMP.lecturers = Lecturer_id

name: Query3
body: SELECT DISTINCT email FROM Lecturer JOIN (SELECT e1.lecturers as lecturers FROM (SELECT * FROM Enrollment WHERE lecturers = 'Huong' ) AS e1 JOIN (SELECT * FROM Enrollment WHERE lecturers = 'Manuel' ) AS e2 ON e1.students = e2.students ) AS TEMP ON TEMP.lecturers = Lecturer_id

name: Query4
body: SELECT Student_id FROM Student WHERE age > 18
